ir Tkachenko, Mikhail Gutseriev || \u2014\n| \n|-\n| Go Alone\n| Dmitry Malikov || Leonid Molochnik, Alexey Zolotarev || \u2014\n| \n|-\n| Grief Does Not Matter\n| Nepara|| Alexey Zolotorev, Leonid Molochnik, Renat Dzhanibekov || \u2014\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year 2014\"\n|-\n| Habitat of Love\n| Rada Rye|| Vyacheslav Klimenkov, Aytekin G. Atas, Soner Akalin || O. Gordeeva, V. Mukhametzyanov\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year 2012\", Winner of the \"\u0421hanson of the Year 2016\"\n|-\n| Happiness Above the Earth\n| Zara || Victor Drobysh, Timofey Leontiev || Alexey Potapenko\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year 2014\"\n|-\n| He and She\n| Alexey Glyzin and Valeriya|| Dmitry Dvoretsky, Vadim Uslanov|| Maasik Hindrek\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year 2016\"\n|-\n| Heavy Heart\n| Polina Gagarina || Alana da Fonseca, Jordan Yaeger || Leonid Kolosovsky \n| The premiere performance at the \"Novaya Volna 2017\", Laureate of \"Song of the Year 2017\" \n|-\n| Hold Love at Gunpoint\n| \"Respublika\" Band || Andrey Ktitarev || \u2014\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year 2016\"\n|-\n| I Am Crying in Vain, Not Parting With You in My Heart\n| Mark Tishman || Andrey Ktitarev, Mikhail Gutseriev|| \u2014\n| \n|-\n| I Am Naughty Because of You\n| Natasha Koroleva and Alexandr Marshal|| Victoria Kokhana|| Alexander Igudin\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year-2014\"\n|-\n| I Am Tired...\n| Natasha Koroleva || Maksim Pokrovsky || \u2014\n| Laureate of the \"Song of the Year 2016\", was performed at the opening of \"Novaya Volna 2016\"\n|-\n| I Did Not Save Our Happiness\n| Avraam Russo \u0438 Rada Rye|| Aytekin G. Atas || \u2014\n| \n|-\n| I Do Not Believe\n| Philipp Kirkorov || Alexey Malakhov || \u2014\n| The premiere performance at the \"Novaya Volna 2017\"\n|-\n| I Hardly Breath\n| Mitya Fomin || Dmitry Dubinsky || \u2014\n| \n|-\n| I Have Only You\n| Natali || Maksim Pokrovsky || Rustam Romanov\n| \n|-\n| I Just Love in Slow Fashion\n| Mikhail Shufutinsky|| Igo